#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (prefillCN), group (CertificateCreationWizard)
#: src/kcfg/settings.kcfg
#, kde-format
msgid "Prefill CN automatically"
msgstr "Προσυμπλήρωσε το CN αυτόματα"

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (prefillCN), group (CertificateCreationWizard)
#: src/kcfg/settings.kcfg
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If true, then the common name (CN) field of S/MIME certificates will be "
"prefilled with information gathered from the system,\n"
"         e.g., from the email settings of the desktop or, on Windows, from "
"the Active Directory."
msgstr ""
"Αν είναι αληθές, τότε το πεδίο του κοινού ονόματος (CN) των πιστοποιητικών S/"
"MIME θα προσυμπληρωθεί με πληροφορίες που έχουν συλλεχθεί από το σύστημα,\n"
"         π.χ., από τις ρυθμίσεις ηλεκτρονικού ταχυδρομείου της επιφάνειας "
"εργασίας ή, σε Windows, από το Active Directory."

#. i18n: ectx: label, entry (prefillSourcesCN), group (CertificateCreationWizard)
#: src/kcfg/settings.kcfg
#, kde-format
msgid "Sources for prefilling CN"
msgstr ""

#. i18n: ectx: whatsthis, entry (prefillSourcesCN), group (CertificateCreationWizard)
#: src/kcfg/settings.kcfg
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This setting specifies from which sources (and with what precedence) the "
"common name (CN) field of newly generated S/MIME certificate signing "
"requests (CSR) shall be prefilled. KEMailSettings uses the name of the "
"desktop's email settings. WinGetUserName (Windows-only) uses the NameDisplay "
"value returned by GetUserNameEx or the value returned by GetUserName. "
"EnvEmail uses the name part of the EMAIL environment variable. ADDisplayName "
"(Windows-only) uses the display name attribute (displayName) retrieved from "
"the Active Directory server. ADFirstNameLastName (Windows-only) uses the "
"first name (givenName) and last name (sn) attributes retrieved from the "
"Active Directory server."
msgstr ""

